resources.string: This application was developed by RemedyConnect. From designing custom websites and mobile apps to providing state-of-the-art digital answering services, RemedyConnect provides a 24/7 presence and voice for private practices, allowing providers to give their patients more convenience and better self-directed care.\n\n

We use a third-party service, Page My Doctor, so you can page the on-call provider with an urgent question after hours. First time users will register first. It’s simple! Please be brief and specific. Pagers and cell phones won’t take long messages easily.
